name: Kisskk
content:
Kisskk was a male Trandoshan, who lived on the planet Cularin during the waning years of the Galactic Republic.
Kisskk was employed as a bodyguard by the Human criminal Vel-Kan. He was present with Vel-Kan in the cantina Spanner's, in the city of Hedrett on Cularin, when the heroes of Cularin visited the bar in about 31 BBY.
